item.title: What does this mean?
item.dc:creator: @RuneRemix RuneRemix
item.description:
@RuneRemix wrote:

ping is short for ping-pong wich the packet is sent its called “ping” when it is received it is called “pong” pinging is just a statistic test it tells you how long between ping and pong. wich is pointless to do on your own computer…
but whatever somone else’s ping is between you will determine there lag.
You can test your ping at speedtest.net
and your upload and download speed determine it…
increase your ul and dl speed and your server wont “lag” as much.

Your welcome.

And dhumiston go to start menu run and type in command
then type in the black box
ping google.com
you can replace google.com with whatever server u wana check.
this can be helpful for deciding wich server to pk on.
the lower the better.
